videos.description: Kansas State's Mike McGuirl gets a steal and passes ahead to David Sloan, who has his layup attempt blocked into the stands by PJ Fuller.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Fuller gets big chasedown block for TCU) 2020/03/11

videos.headline: Fuller gets big chasedown block for TCU

videos.description: Mike McGuirl dishes to Makol Mawien, who scores in traffic underneath the basket for the go-ahead score in Kansas State's 53-49 win over TCU.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Mawien's late bucket puts Kansas State ahead for good) 2020/03/11

videos.headline: Mawien's late bucket puts Kansas State ahead for good
